Strafe nears the other Technobots, breaking in between Scattershot and
Nosecone, "Finally, some action, to get the old pistons pumpin. Action
to stretch out our joints, action..." he kept rambling. 

"Yes. It seems like a paramount oportunity to explore the great reaches
of space." he said reflectivly, looking out the window to the stars,
noticing thei Magnificence.

Grimlock walked over to the window. "Hmmmmmmmmmm, what you think of this
Swoop, Snarl (Kslawdogg). Chance to revisit earth." he said, for the
first time ignoring the Autobots.

Hoist walked up to Pacifix. "So chief, how's it feel?" he asked,
genuinly curious.
